Who was it play'd the Gardener, (sure it could not be honest Searle
               Mr. Pope's Gardener at Twickenham.
               ) in Lopping some Branches, Inoculating others, and Transplanting a large Shoot from one of your Letters to Mr. Cromwell, and Graffing it upon Mr. Walsh's Stock?

